Install the PyGTK (http://aruiz.typepad.com/siliconisland/2006/12/allinone_win32_.html) all-in-one package and
Twisted (http://tmrc.mit.edu/mirror/twisted/Twisted/2.5/Twisted_NoDocs-2.5.0.win32-py2.5.exe).

